+  tcpsock:setoption
+    syntax: *tcpsock:setoption(option, value?)*
+
+    context: *rewrite_by_lua*, access_by_lua*, content_by_lua*, ngx.timer.**
+
+    This function is added for LuaSocket
+    (<http://w3.impa.br/~diego/software/luasocket/tcp.html>) API
