+See also [ngx.shared.DICT.flush_expired](http://wiki.nginx.org/HttpLuaModule#ngx.shared.DICT.flush_expired) and [ngx.shared.DICT](http://wiki.nginx.org/HttpLuaModule#ngx.shared.DICT).
